      • finishSpecifyingOutput

        public void finishSpecifyingOutput(java.lang.String transformName,
                                   PInput input,
                                   PTransform<?,?> transform)
        Description copied from interface: POutput
        As part of applying the producing PTransform, finalizes this output to make it ready for being used as an input and for running.

        This includes ensuring that all PCollections have Coders specified or defaulted.

        Automatically invoked whenever this POutput is output, after POutput.finishSpecifyingOutput(String, PInput, PTransform) has been called on each component PValue returned by POutput.expand().

        Specified by:
